<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us - Coding Website</title>
<style>
    body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  background-color: #f4f4f4;
  color: #333;
}

.container {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 20px auto;
  padding: 20px;
  background-color: #fff;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

header h1 {
  font-size: 2.5em;
  color: #333;
}

.about {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.team-photo {
  flex: 1 1 300px;
  max-width: 300px;
  margin-right: 20px;
  border-radius: 8px;
}

.about-text {
  flex: 2 1 500px;
}

.about-text h2 {
  color: #333;
  margin-top: 0;
}

.about-text p,
.about-text ul {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.about-text ul {
  list-style-type: disc;
  padding-left: 20px;
}

footer {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding-top: 10px;
  border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
}

footer p {
  margin: 0;
  color: #666;
}



/* for navbar*/

/*navigation bar */

/* Navbar container */
/* Reset some default styles */
ul {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  list-style-type: none;
}

/* Navbar container */
.navbar {
  background-color: black;
  padding: 14px 10px;
  
  font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  position: fixed
  top: 0;
  width: 100%;
  z-index: 1000;
}

/* Navbar links container */
.navbar ul {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  align-items: center;
}

/* Navbar links */
.navbar ul li a {
  color: #f9f8f8;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 14px 20px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 17px;
}

/* Change color on hover */
.navbar ul li a:hover {
  background-color: #ddd;
  color: black;
}




</style>
</head>
<body>
{{> navbar}}

  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>About Us</h1>
    </header>
    <section class="about">
      <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/570ebc54e32140a560e3d6d4/1610738838099-F36MYQU07CGHTKXFP941/codieclear.png" alt="Coding Team" class="team-photo">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>We are a passionate team of developers, educators, and tech enthusiasts dedicated to helping you start your coding journey. Our mission is to provide high-quality, accessible, and engaging coding education to learners of all levels.</p>
        
        <h2>Our Courses</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Python Programming: Master one of the most versatile and in-demand programming languages in the industry.</li>
          <li>Web Development: Build dynamic websites and web applications using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and more.</li>
          <li>Data Science: Dive into the world of data analysis and machine learning with Python and R.</li>
          <li>Mobile App Development: Learn to build native and cross-platform mobile apps for iOS and Android.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to provide high-quality services to our customers and create a positive impact in the community. We believe in the power of technology to change lives and are committed to helping our students achieve their goals.</p>
        
        <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@example.com">info@example.com</a> for any inquiries.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2024 Coding Website. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
